      <odd id="aspace_a8511725ccb5e6432956af019bc55ccc">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 5-D (YRG 5-D), Investment and insurance records of Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_5e3b103511b1562833b1aa7fe4de361e">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.  Files restricted to the office of origin only have been redacted from the finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_5b167aaff44f497495d1d1599b51cd2a">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
